==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sheepberry
<hw>Sheep"ber`ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The edible fruit of a small North American tree of the genus
<gen>Viburnum</gen> (<spn>Viburnum Lentago</spn>), having white flowers
in flat cymes; also, the tree itself. Called also
<altname>nannyberry</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sheepbite</ent>⟦br⟧
